--   FY2024: fy2024_q4xprxex991.htm (full year + Q4 actuals)\
--   FY2025: fy2025_q2, q3, q4 press releases (SEC EDGAR)\
-- Segments updated to match Disney's current taxonomy:\
--   Entertainment, Sports (ESPN), Experiences\
-- Revenue figures: exact from SEC filings (millions USD)\
